PrecisReappointment of SONIA L'HEUREUX of North Gower, Ontario, as a Parliamentary Librarian on an interim basis, to hold office during pleasure for a term of one year or until such time as a Parliamentary Librarian is appointed, whichever is earlier, effective June 21, 2017.
